            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>This tender comprise the provision of 3 Managers who shall perform the following services in regard to Construction Management and site supervision; A Contract Manager, a Discipline Manager for the Substructures and a Discipline Manager for Superstructure for the construction of the new Storstrøm Bridge.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="EUR">15200000.00</VAL_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
